lenders.name: Mazarine
lenders.loan_because:
According to The Spirit Level, when we are unequal, we are all suffering.

There are 100 million missing women in the world, according to economist Amrita Sen. This is due to women not being valued as much as men all over the world. Studies have shown that when you educate a girl, poverty rates drop. Women that we lend to on Kiva will put their money back into their communities and educate their children, and lift up everyone. I want to help women all over the world empower themselves. This is also why I wrote my book, The Wild Woman's Guide to Fundraising.
lenders.occupational_info: Every week I get to teach nonprofits how to raise more money! I'm very grateful for my life!
